      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean u said it's debated, but like, isn't it pretty well documented that these laws mostly just end up hurting marginalized people more than they actually stop crime? feels like the \"deterrence\" side is kind of an old way of thinking that doesn't hold up to modern data.",
